H3.text: who caused to build qutub minar in delhi. Iltutmish

A4.text: Qutb-ud-din Aibak initiated the construction of the victory tower, but only managed to finish the first level.

A5.text: Aibak's successor and son-in-law Shamsuddin Iltutmish completed a further three stories.

A6.text: The construction of the Qutb Minar in Delhi started during Aibak's reign.

A7.text: Aibak is known for having commissioned the Qutb Minar in Delhi, and the Adhai Din Ka Jhonpra in Ajmer.
